subtitle: Albany Brigham
content:
Halloween is enveloping the city in its gruesome glow and GTA+ Members can revel in the season's trappings by claiming the new Albany Brigham (Muscle) at The Vinewood Car Club through November 8.

GTA+ Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
